text: Tanzim Hasan Sakib (born 20 October 2002) is a Bangladeshi cricketer. He made his List A debut for Bangladesh Krira Shikkha Protishtan in the 2018–19 Dhaka Premier Division Cricket League on 27 March 2019. In December 2019, he was named in Bangladesh's squad for the 2020 Under-19 Cricket World Cup. ==References== ==External links== * Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:Bangladeshi cricketers Category:Bangladesh Krira Shikkha Protishtan cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
